videos.headline: Brown turns short completion into 84-yard TD
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu swings it out to A.J. Brown, who breaks a tackle and shows off his blazing speed on the Rebels' longest touchdown of the season.

videos.headline: Vanderbilt blocks punt for safety
videos.description: DB Max Worship breaks through the line and gets to Mac Brown's punt, sending the ball out of the end zone for a safety.

videos.headline: Vanderbilt draws closer before halftime
videos.description: Kyle Shurmur throws of bubble screen to Kalija Lipscomb, who fights his way across the goal line to narrow the Rebels' lead to 14-13 before the end of the first half.

videos.headline: Vaughn puts Vanderbilt ahead with 1-yard TD run
videos.description: Ke'Shawn Vaughn gets to the outside and powers across the goal line to give the Commodores their first lead of the night, 19-13.

videos.headline: Shurmur breaks tie with 3-yard TD pass
videos.description: Kyle Shurmur throws a strike over the middle to C.J. Bolar, who makes the catch in the end zone to give the Commodores a 26-19 lead.

videos.headline: Lodge ties game with ridiculous one-handed catch
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu throws a back-shoulder pass to DaMarkus Lodge, who reaches out with one hand to make the grab and tie the score at 26-26.

videos.headline: Vanderbilt intercepts Ta'amu in end zone
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu launches a pass to the end zone, but Joejuan Williams makes the leaping interception to protect the Commodores' 29-26 lead.

videos.headline: Shurmur starts off OT with 5-yard TD pass
videos.description: Kyle Shurmur throws on target to Kalija Lipscomb, who goes down low to make the grab and put the Commodores ahead 36-29 in the extra frame.

videos.headline: Williams seals Commodores' win in OT with pass break-up
videos.description: Kyle Shurmur goes to the end zone on 4th-and-6, but Joejuan Williams lays out to knock the ball down and secure a 36-29 win for Vanderbilt in overtime.
